divs: Sighting Detailsi am in laguna niguel. I was looking roughly south east when i saw a bright fireball that had a bright green glow around it- fly through the sky for a couple seconds. It looked a lot like a falling star but much larger and brighter. It also looked as if it were very close which could have been because of the size. Strangely enough it truly had a bright green glow. Anyone see it??
Summary: Green fireball flying through the sky for a couple seconds till what it seemed a burn out
